thread.title_full: Rush Order Tees reviewed by Deanna

author: Deanna
title: Deanna
text: They probably have the best deals online, that i've seen ordered from then in the past and got a great deal on a large order. I decided to order again with this company and a new representative Josh told me he wasn't able to give me the deal I got previously but was able to work with getting me the best deal he could fetch for me. i will most definitely keep ordering shirts from this company.
